w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont"/><dcterms:hasPart>Eighth Miracle: The Resurrection: How Christ rose from the dead and how many others were raised and went to Jerusalem and preached about Jesus Christ </dcterms:hasPart><crm:P57_has_number_of_parts rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">0</crm:P57_has_number_of_parts><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/><betmas:locusTo/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP00648/msitem/ms_i2.9"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont"/><dcterms:hasPart>Ninth Miracle: The Ascension: How Jesus gathered the disciples at Däbrä Zäyt, promised the Holy Spirit and ascended to heaven </dcterms:hasPart><crm:P57_has_number_of_parts rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">0</crm:P57_has_number_of_parts><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/><betmas:locusTo/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP00648/quire/q1"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP00648"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/quire"/><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/><betmas:locusTo/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus><crm:P43_has_dimension><crm:E54_Dimension><crm:P90_has_value>2</crm:P90_has_value><crm:P91_has_unit>leaf</crm:P91_has_unit></crm:E54_Dimension></crm:P43_has_dimension></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP00648/quire/q2"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMIP00648"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/quire"/><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/><betmas:locusTo/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus><crm:P43_has_dimension><crm:E54_Dimension><crm:P90_has_value>8</crm:P90_has_value><crm:P91_has_unit>leaf</crm:P91_has_unit></crm:E54_Dimension></crm:P43_has_dimension></rdf:Descr